episodes.title: How I was Controlled and Harassed by a Mind-controlling Cult!
episodes.description:
How a mind-controlling cult such as Jehovah's witnesses control you and what it can lead to.

This is part of my story and what has happened to me being born into and grew up and lived most of my life as a Jehovah's witness. 

#exjw #exjehovahswitness #mindcontrol #cult
#jehovahswitness
